'''2016年薩摩亞大選'''在2016年3月4日举行，以選出[[薩摩亞議會|薩摩亞議會]]的49個議席，大約有116,000人登記為選民<ref name="MT">{{cite web|last1=Timutimu|first1=Ripeka|title=Easy victory predicted for Tuilaepa|url=https://www.maoritelevision.com/news/regional/easy-victory-predicted-tuilaepa|publisher=[[Māori_Television|Māori Television]]|accessdate=5 March 2016|date=4 March 2016|archive-date=2016-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729214144/https://www.maoritelevision.com/news/regional/easy-victory-predicted-tuilaepa|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==選舉制度==
議員由35個單議席選區和7個雙議席選區選出。議席以[[領先者當選|領先者當選]]，雙議席選區的選民可投兩票。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2351_B.htm |title=Samoa (Fono) Electoral system |publisher=[[Inter-Parliamentary_Union|Inter-Parliamentary Union]] |access-date=5 March 2016 |archive-date=2017-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803113912/http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2351_B.htm }}</ref>2013年通過的憲法修正法案保證議會最少有10%的議席由女性出任<ref>{{cite news|title=Constitution Amendment Act 2013|url=http://www.ilo.org/dyn/natlex/docs/ELECTRONIC/93576/109441/F-316467409/WSM93576%20Eng.pdf|accessdate=5 March 2016|agency=[[International_Labour_Organization|International Labour Organization]]|archive-date=2017-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171207143522/http://www.ilo.org/dyn/natlex/docs/ELECTRONIC/93576/109441/F-316467409/WSM93576%20Eng.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，如果當選的女性議員不足10%，額外席位將給予得票率最高的女性敗選者以增加女性議員人數。

==選舉結果==
由於49名當選議員只有4名是女性，額外1席給予得票率最高的女性敗選者以滿足至少10%議員是女性的規定<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.state.gov/reports/2020-country-reports-on-human-rights-practices/samoa/ |title=2020 Country Reports on Human Rights Practices: Samoa |access-date=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525092314/https://www.state.gov/reports/2020-country-reports-on-human-rights-practices/samoa/ }}</ref>。當選的13名無黨籍人士中，有12人在選舉後加入人權保護黨<ref>{{cite web |url=https://freedomhouse.org/country/samoa/freedom-world/2020 |title=Samoa: Freedom in the World 2020 Country Report |publisher=Freedom House |accessdate=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524234316/https://freedomhouse.org/country/samoa/freedom-world/2020 }}</ref>。

